      "description": "Ratiometric Raman analysis of reversible thia-Michael reactions was achieved using alpha-cyanoacrylic acid derivatives. Among alpha-cyanoacrylic acid derivatives, the smallest derivative, ThioRas, and its glutathione adduct were simultaneously detected in various subcellular locations using Raman microscopy.",
